    "description": "Bubble hunt - a game in which you need to pop bubbles with the help of a gorpoon on a chain. By collecting points for bursting bubbles, you can get extra lives.<br />\r\nA double horn can also fall out, which will help to deal with bubbles twice as efficiently. There are several types of bubbles.<br />\r\nSome fly according to the laws of physics, but some fly bouncing off walls, others fall apart. You need to look for your own approach to each IP.<br />\r\nThe seemingly simple gameplay is actually quite difficult. You need attentiveness, dexterity and ingenuity to win.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n-Beautiful graphics<br />\r\n<br />\r\n-Interesting gameplay<br />\r\n<br />\r\n-Difficult levels",
